in.teramatrix.googleservices.util

Class UrlManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • in.teramatrix.googleservices.util.UrlManager

  • public class UrlManager
extends java.lang.Object
    A collection of all the APIs used in this project. In case of any updates in URL, only this file can be modified. At this time, this file contains following Apis...
    • Geocoding
    • Reverse Geocoding
    • Places Api
    • Directions Api
    • Distance Matrix Api
    Author:
    Mohsin Khan
    Date:
    3/21/2016

      • getAppendedString

        private static java.lang.String getAppendedString(java.lang.String separator,
                                                  java.lang.String... params)
        This method will form all the array elements separated using seprator like pipeline "|". For example if array consists of "hotel", "restaurant", "bar" then these items will be converted as "hotel|restaurant|bar"
        Parameters:
        params - array of place types to be search
        Returns:
        a single string of all items
